hadiths[231]{hadithnumber,text}:
5938,Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se pachhney lagwaaney ke mutaalliq ijazat talab ki to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat abu-Taiba (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke unhein pachhney lagaaein. unhon-ne (Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : Hazrat abu taiba (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke dudh-sharik bhai they ya nabaligh ladkey they. (aur unhon-ne hath ya paon aisi jagah pachhney lagaey jinhein dekhna mehram ya bachchey ke liye jaaiz hai.)
5939,Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se pachhney lagwaaney ke mutaalliq ijazat talab ki to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat abu-Taiba (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke unhein pachhney lagaaein. unhon-ne (Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : Hazrat abu taiba (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke dudh-sharik bhai they ya nabaligh ladkey they. (aur unhon-ne hath ya paon aisi jagah pachhney lagaey jinhein dekhna mehram ya bachchey ke liye jaaiz hai.)
5940,"abu-Muawia ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (jab (Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) (ko jange-khandaq ke mauqe par hath ki badi rag par zakhm laga to un) ke paas aik tabeeb bheja, us ne unki (zakhmi) rag (ki kharaab ho janey wali jagah) kaati, phir is par dagh lagaya (taake khoon ruk jaey.)"
5941,"abu-Muawia ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (jab (Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) (ko jange-khandaq ke mauqe par hath ki badi rag par zakhm laga to un) ke paas aik tabeeb bheja, us ne unki (zakhmi) rag (ki kharaab ho janey wali jagah) kaati, phir is par dagh lagaya (taake khoon ruk jaey.)"
5942,Jarir aur Sufiyan donon ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath bayan kya aur to unki rag kaati ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye.
5943,Jarir aur Sufiyan donon ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath bayan kya aur to unki rag kaati ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye.
5944,"Sulaiman ne kaha : maine abu Sufiyan ko suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : jange-Ehzaab mein Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ke bazu ki badi rag mein teer laga. kaha : to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein dagh lagwaaya."
5945,"Sulaiman ne kaha : maine abu Sufiyan ko suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : jange-Ehzaab mein Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ke bazu ki badi rag mein teer laga. kaha : to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein dagh lagwaaya."
5946,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ke bazu ki badi rag mein teer laga, kaha : to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se teer ke phal ke sath us (jagah) ko dagh lagaya, unka hath dobara sooj gaya to aap ne dobara is par dagh lagaya ."
5947,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ke bazu ki badi rag mein teer laga, kaha : to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se teer ke phal ke sath us (jagah) ko dagh lagaya, unka hath dobara sooj gaya to aap ne dobara is par dagh lagaya ."
5948,Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pachhney lagwaaney aur lagaaney waley ko uski ujrat di aur aap ne naak ke zariey dawaai li.
5949,Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pachhney lagwaaney aur lagaaney waley ko uski ujrat di aur aap ne naak ke zariey dawaai li.
5950,"Amr bin Aamir Ansari ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, aap keh rahe they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pachhney bhi lagwaaey, aap kisi ki ujrat ke mamley mein kisi par zarra barabar zulm nahi kartey they ( balke zyada ata farmatey they.)"
5951,"Amr bin Aamir Ansari ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, aap keh rahe they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pachhney bhi lagwaaey, aap kisi ki ujrat ke mamley mein kisi par zarra barabar zulm nahi kartey they ( balke zyada ata farmatey they.)"
5952,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Ubaidullah se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bukhar jahannam ki lapton se hai, usko pani se thanda karo."
5953,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Ubaidullah se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bukhar jahannam ki lapton se hai, usko pani se thanda karo."
5954,"Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bukhar ki shiddat jahannam ki lapton se hai, usko pani se thanda karo."
5955,"Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bukhar ki shiddat jahannam ki lapton se hai, usko pani se thanda karo."
5956,"Imam Malik aur Zuhhaak bin Usman, donon ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bukhar jahannam ki lapton mein se hai, usko pani se bujhaao."
5957,"Imam Malik aur Zuhhaak bin Usman, donon ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bukhar jahannam ki lapton mein se hai, usko pani se bujhaao."
5958,"Muhammad-bin Zaid ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bukhar jahannam ki lapton se hai, usko pani se bujhaao."
5959,"Muhammad-bin Zaid ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bukhar jahannam ki lapton se hai, usko pani se bujhaao."
5960,"ibne-Numair ne Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bukhar jahannam ki lapton se hai usko pani se thanda karo."
5961,"ibne-Numair ne Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bukhar jahannam ki lapton se hai usko pani se thanda karo."
5962,Khalid-bin Haris aur Abda bin Sulaiman ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5963,Khalid-bin Haris aur Abda bin Sulaiman ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5964,"Abda bin Sulaiman ne Hisham se, unhon-ne Fatima se, unhon-ne Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke bukhar mein mubtala aurat ko unke paas laya jata to wo pani mangwaatin aur usey aurat ke garebaan mein undeltin aur kehtin : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is (bukhaar) ko pani se thanda karo aur kaha (wo kehtin :) ye jahannam ki lapton se hai."
5965,"Abda bin Sulaiman ne Hisham se, unhon-ne Fatima se, unhon-ne Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke bukhar mein mubtala aurat ko unke paas laya jata to wo pani mangwaatin aur usey aurat ke garebaan mein undeltin aur kehtin : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is (bukhaar) ko pani se thanda karo aur kaha (wo kehtin :) ye jahannam ki lapton se hai."
5966,"ibne-Numair aur abu-Usama ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur ibne-Numair ki hadis mein hai : wo iske aur uski qamees ke garebaan ke darmyan pani daaltin. abu-Usama ki hadis mein unhon-ne ye jahannam ki lapton mein se hai ka zikr nahi kya. abwaa hamd ne kaha : Ibrahim ne kaha : hamein Hasan-bin-Bishr ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki."
5967,"ibne-Numair aur abu-Usama ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur ibne-Numair ki hadis mein hai : wo iske aur uski qamees ke garebaan ke darmyan pani daaltin. abu-Usama ki hadis mein unhon-ne ye jahannam ki lapton mein se hai ka zikr nahi kya. abwaa hamd ne kaha : Ibrahim ne kaha : hamein Hasan-bin-Bishr ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki."
5968,"Saeed bin Masruq ne abaaya bin Rifaa se, unhon-ne apne dada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : bukhar jahannam ke josh se hai, usko pani se thanda karo."
5969,"Saeed bin Masruq ne abaaya bin Rifaa se, unhon-ne apne dada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : bukhar jahannam ke josh se hai, usko pani se thanda karo."
5970,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Muhammad-bin-Musanna , Muhammad-bin-Hatim aur Abu-Bakar bin Naafe ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Abaya bin Rifaa se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : bukhar jahannam ke josh se hai, usey khud se pani ke zariey thanda karo. (Abu-Bakar) ki riwayat mein khud se ke alfaz nahi hain. neez Abu-Bakar ne kaha ke Abaya bin Rifaa ne ( حدثنی ke bajaey) ( اخبرني Rafe-bin-Khadeej ( kaha."
5971,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Muhammad-bin-Musanna , Muhammad-bin-Hatim aur Abu-Bakar bin Naafe ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Abaya bin Rifaa se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : bukhar jahannam ke josh se hai, usey khud se pani ke zariey thanda karo. (Abu-Bakar) ki riwayat mein khud se ke alfaz nahi hain. neez Abu-Bakar ne kaha ke Abaya bin Rifaa ne ( حدثنی ke bajaey) ( اخبرني Rafe-bin-Khadeej ( kaha."
5972,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke marz mein ham ne aap ki marzi ke baghair munh ke koney se aap ke dehane-mubarak mein dawaai dali, aap ne ishaarey se roka bhi ke mujhey zabardasti dawaai na pilao, ham ne ( aapas mein) kaha : ye mareez ki tabai taur par dawai ki na-pasandidgi (ki wjah se) hai. jab aapko fayda hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi na bachey, sab ko zabardasti (hi) dawai pilaai jaey, siwaey Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke kyonke wo tumharey sath maujood nahi they."
5973,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke marz mein ham ne aap ki marzi ke baghair munh ke koney se aap ke dehane-mubarak mein dawaai dali, aap ne ishaarey se roka bhi ke mujhey zabardasti dawaai na pilao, ham ne ( aapas mein) kaha : ye mareez ki tabai taur par dawai ki na-pasandidgi (ki wjah se) hai. jab aapko fayda hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi na bachey, sab ko zabardasti (hi) dawai pilaai jaey, siwaey Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke kyonke wo tumharey sath maujood nahi they."
5974,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Ukasha bin Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan umme-Qais binte-Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : main apne betey ko lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui jisne (abhi tak) khana shuru nahi kya tha, us ne aap par peshab kar diya to aap ne pani manga kar is par baha diya."
5975,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Ukasha bin Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan umme-Qais binte-Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : main apne betey ko lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui jisne (abhi tak) khana shuru nahi kya tha, us ne aap par peshab kar diya to aap ne pani manga kar is par baha diya."
5976,"unhon-ne ( Umme- Qais (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : main apne aik bachchey ko lekar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui, maine uske galey mein sozish ki bina par iske halaq ko ungli se uper ki taraf dabaaya tha (taake sozish ki wjah se latka hua hissey uper ho jaey) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ungliyon ke dabaaw ke zariey se apne bachchon ka gala kyon dabaati ho? (aap ne bachchon ke liye us takleef-deh tareeqae-ilaaj ko na-pasand farmaya, ( tum aud-hindi ka istemal lazim kar lo. usmein saat (7) iqsaam ki shifa hai unmein se aik nimoniya hai. halaq ki sozish ke liye usko naak ke rastey istemal kya jata hai. aur nimoniye ke liye usey munh mein undela jata hai."
5977,"unhon-ne ( Umme- Qais (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : main apne aik bachchey ko lekar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui, maine uske galey mein sozish ki bina par iske halaq ko ungli se uper ki taraf dabaaya tha (taake sozish ki wjah se latka hua hissey uper ho jaey) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ungliyon ke dabaaw ke zariey se apne bachchon ka gala kyon dabaati ho? (aap ne bachchon ke liye us takleef-deh tareeqae-ilaaj ko na-pasand farmaya, ( tum aud-hindi ka istemal lazim kar lo. usmein saat (7) iqsaam ki shifa hai unmein se aik nimoniya hai. halaq ki sozish ke liye usko naak ke rastey istemal kya jata hai. aur nimoniye ke liye usey munh mein undela jata hai."
5978,"Yunus bin Yazeed ne kaha ke ibne-Shahab ne unhein bataya, kaha : mujhey Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah-bin Utba-bin- Masood ne khabar di ke Hazrat umme-Qais binte-Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) . pahley pahal hijrat karne wali un khawaateen mein se thin jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath bait ki thi. ye banu-Asad-bin Khuzaima ke fard Hazrat Ukasha bin Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan thin. kaha : unhon-ne mujhey khabar di ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main apne aik betey ko lekar aaein jo abhi khana khaney ki umr ko nahi pahuncha tha, unhon-ne galey ki sozish ki bina par iske halaq ko ungli se dabaaya tha. Yunus ne kaha halaq dabaaya tha. yani ungli chubhoi thi (taake faasid khoon nikal jaey) unhein ye khof tha ke uske galey mein sozish hai. unhon ( Umme- Qais (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is ungli chubhoney waley tareeqey se tum apne bachchon ka gala kyon dabaati ho? is aud-hindi yani kust ka istemal karo kyonke usmein saat (7) iqsaam ki shifa hai unmein se aik nimoniya ."
5979,"Yunus bin Yazeed ne kaha ke ibne-Shahab ne unhein bataya, kaha : mujhey Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah-bin Utba-bin- Masood ne khabar di ke Hazrat umme-Qais binte-Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) . pahley pahal hijrat karne wali un khawaateen mein se thin jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath bait ki thi. ye banu-Asad-bin Khuzaima ke fard Hazrat Ukasha bin Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan thin. kaha : unhon-ne mujhey khabar di ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main apne aik betey ko lekar aaein jo abhi khana khaney ki umr ko nahi pahuncha tha, unhon-ne galey ki sozish ki bina par iske halaq ko ungli se dabaaya tha. Yunus ne kaha halaq dabaaya tha. yani ungli chubhoi thi (taake faasid khoon nikal jaey) unhein ye khof tha ke uske galey mein sozish hai. unhon ( Umme- Qais (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is ungli chubhoney waley tareeqey se tum apne bachchon ka gala kyon dabaati ho? is aud-hindi yani kust ka istemal karo kyonke usmein saat (7) iqsaam ki shifa hai unmein se aik nimoniya ."
5980,Ubaidullah ne kaha : unhon ( Umme- Qais (Raziallahu anhu)) ne mujh se bayan kya ke unke usi bachchey ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki god mein peshab kar diya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani mangwa kar is par baha diya tha aur usko zyada ragad kar nahi dhoya tha.
5981,Ubaidullah ne kaha : unhon ( Umme- Qais (Raziallahu anhu)) ne mujh se bayan kya ke unke usi bachchey ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki god mein peshab kar diya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani mangwa kar is par baha diya tha aur usko zyada ragad kar nahi dhoya tha.
5982,"Aqeel ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman aur Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne un donon ko khabar di ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna, shoneez saam ( maut (ke ilawa har bimari se shifa hai. saam : maut hai aur hiba Sauda (se murad) shoneez (zeera siyah) hai."
5983,"Aqeel ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman aur Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne un donon ko khabar di ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna, shoneez saam ( maut (ke ilawa har bimari se shifa hai. saam : maut hai aur hiba Sauda (se murad) shoneez (zeera siyah) hai."
5984,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Sufiyan-bin-Uena Mamar aur Shuaib sab ne Zohri se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Aqeel ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki. Sufiyan aur Yunus ki hadis mein al-Hibatus-Sauda ke alfaz hain unhon-ne ( aagey ( shoneez nahi kaha."
5985,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Sufiyan-bin-Uena Mamar aur Shuaib sab ne Zohri se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Aqeel ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki. Sufiyan aur Yunus ki hadis mein al-Hibatus-Sauda ke alfaz hain unhon-ne ( aagey ( shoneez nahi kaha."
5986,"Alaa (bin Abdur-Rehman (ke walid ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maut ke siwa koi bimari nahi jiski shoneez ke zariey se shifa na hoti ho."
5987,"Alaa (bin Abdur-Rehman (ke walid ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maut ke siwa koi bimari nahi jiski shoneez ke zariey se shifa na hoti ho."
5988,"Urwa ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke jab unke khandan mein se kisi fard ka intiqal hota to auratein ( uski taziyat ke liye) jama ho jaatin, phir unke ghar waley aur khawaas reh jatey aur baqi log chaley jatey, us waqt wo talbiney ki aik handi (degchi) pakaaney ko kehtin talbeena pakaya jata, phir sareed banaya jata aur is par talbina daala jata, phir wo kehtin : ye khaao kyonke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna, talbina bimar ke dil ko raahat bakhshtaa hai aur gham ko halka karta hai."
5989,"Urwa ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke jab unke khandan mein se kisi fard ka intiqal hota to auratein ( uski taziyat ke liye) jama ho jaatin, phir unke ghar waley aur khawaas reh jatey aur baqi log chaley jatey, us waqt wo talbiney ki aik handi (degchi) pakaaney ko kehtin talbeena pakaya jata, phir sareed banaya jata aur is par talbina daala jata, phir wo kehtin : ye khaao kyonke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna, talbina bimar ke dil ko raahat bakhshtaa hai aur gham ko halka karta hai."
5990,"Shoba ne Qatada se, unhon-ne abu mutawakkil se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik shakhs hazir hua aur kaha : mere bhai ka pet chal pada hai) dast lag gaey. hain) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usko shehad pilao. us ne usey shehad pilaya, wo phir aaya aur kaha : maine usey shehad pilaya hai, us se (daston ki tezi mein) mazeed izafa ho gaya hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen baar us se wahi farmaya (shehad pilao) jab wo chothi baar aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey shehad pilao. usne kaha : maine usey shehad pilaya hai us se daston mein izaafey ke ilawa aur kuchh nahi hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ne sach farmaya hai (ke shehad mein shifa hai) aur tumharey bhai ka pet jhoot bol raha hai. us ne usey (aur) shehad pilaya wo tandurust ho gaya."
