5994,""" "" "" "" "" "" Imam Malik ne Muhammad-bin Munkadir aur Umar-bin Ubaidullah ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Nazar se, unhon-ne Aamir bin ( Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne suna ke wo Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se poochh rahe they. aap ne taaoon ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya suna, ? Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : taaoon ( Allah ki bheji hui ( aafat ya azab hai jo Bani-Israeel par bheja gaya ya ( farmaya ( tum se pahley logon par bheja gaya jab tum suno ke wo kisi sar zamin mein hai to us sar zamin par na jao aur agar wo aisi sar zamin mein waaqe ho jaey jis main tum log ( maujood (ho to tum us se bhag kar wahan se na niklo . abu-Nazar ne (ye jumla ( kaha : tumhen us ( taaoon ( se faraar ke ilawa koi aur baat (is sar zamin se) na nikal rahi ho. "" "" "" "" "" "" "" """
