5996,"Abdullaah-bin-Muslima bin Qanab aur Quteba bin Saeed ne kaha : hamein Mughira bin Abdur-Rehman qarshi ne abu-Nazar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aamir bin Sad-bin-abi-Waqas se, unhon-ne Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : taaoon azab ki alamat hai, Allah Taala ne apne bandon mein kuchh logon ko taaoon mein mubtlaa kiya , jab tum taaoon ke barey mein suno to wahan mat jao aur jab us sarzameen mein taaoon phail jaey jahan tum ho to wahan se mat bhaago . ye Qanabi ki hadis hai, Quteba ne bhi is tarah bayan kya hai."
5997,"Abdullaah-bin-Muslima bin Qanab aur Quteba bin Saeed ne kaha : hamein Mughira bin Abdur-Rehman qarshi ne abu-Nazar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aamir bin Sad-bin-abi-Waqas se, unhon-ne Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : taaoon azab ki alamat hai, Allah Taala ne apne bandon mein kuchh logon ko taaoon mein mubtlaa kiya , jab tum taaoon ke barey mein suno to wahan mat jao aur jab us sarzameen mein taaoon phail jaey jahan tum ho to wahan se mat bhaago . ye Qanabi ki hadis hai, Quteba ne bhi is tarah bayan kya hai."
5998,"Sufiyan ne Muhammad-bin Munkadir se, unhon-ne Aamir-bin-Sad se, unhon-ne Usama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye taaoon aik azab hai jo tum se pahley logon par musallat kya gaya tha, ya ( farmaya : ( Bani-Israeel par musallat kya gaya tha, agar ye kisi ilaaqey mein ho to tum us se bhag kar wahan se na nikalna aur agar kisi (doosri ( sarzameen main ( taaoon ( maujood ho to tum usmein dakhil na hona ."
5999,"Sufiyan ne Muhammad-bin Munkadir se, unhon-ne Aamir-bin-Sad se, unhon-ne Usama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye taaoon aik azab hai jo tum se pahley logon par musallat kya gaya tha, ya ( farmaya : ( Bani-Israeel par musallat kya gaya tha, agar ye kisi ilaaqey mein ho to tum us se bhag kar wahan se na nikalna aur agar kisi (doosri ( sarzameen main ( taaoon ( maujood ho to tum usmein dakhil na hona ."
6000,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Dinar ne bataya ke Aamir-bin-Sad ne unhein khabar di ke kisi shakhs ne Hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas se taaoon ke barey mein sawal kya to ( wahan maujood (Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main tumhen iske barey mein bataata hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye aik azab ya saza hai jisey Allah Taala ne Bani-Israeel ke aik garoh par bheja tha, ya (farmaya :) un logon par jo tum se pehley they, lihaza tum jab kisi sarzameen mein iske (phailney ke) mutaalliq suno to usmein iske hotey huey dakhil na hona aur jab ye tum par waarid ho jaey to us se bhaga karo wahan se na nikalna."
6001,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Dinar ne bataya ke Aamir-bin-Sad ne unhein khabar di ke kisi shakhs ne Hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas se taaoon ke barey mein sawal kya to ( wahan maujood (Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main tumhen iske barey mein bataata hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye aik azab ya saza hai jisey Allah Taala ne Bani-Israeel ke aik garoh par bheja tha, ya (farmaya :) un logon par jo tum se pehley they, lihaza tum jab kisi sarzameen mein iske (phailney ke) mutaalliq suno to usmein iske hotey huey dakhil na hona aur jab ye tum par waarid ho jaey to us se bhaga karo wahan se na nikalna."
6002,Hammad-bin-Zaid aur Sufiyan-bin-Uena donon ne Amr-bin-Dinar se ibne-Juraij ki sanad ke sath usi ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
6003,Hammad-bin-Zaid aur Sufiyan-bin-Uena donon ne Amr-bin-Dinar se ibne-Juraij ki sanad ke sath usi ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
6004,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Aamir-bin-Sad se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki : ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye bimari (taaoon aik) azab hai jo tum se pahley aik ummat ko hua tha. phir wo zamin mein reh gaya. kabhi chala jata hai, kabhi phir aata hai. lihaza jo koi kisi mulk mein suney ke wahan taaoon hai, to wo wahan na jaey aur jab uske mulk mein taaoon namudaar ho to wahan se bhaagey bhi nahi."
6005,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Aamir-bin-Sad se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki : ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye bimari (taaoon aik) azab hai jo tum se pahley aik ummat ko hua tha. phir wo zamin mein reh gaya. kabhi chala jata hai, kabhi phir aata hai. lihaza jo koi kisi mulk mein suney ke wahan taaoon hai, to wo wahan na jaey aur jab uske mulk mein taaoon namudaar ho to wahan se bhaagey bhi nahi."
6006,Mamar ne Zohri se Yunus ki sanad ke sath usi (Yunus) ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
6007,Mamar ne Zohri se Yunus ki sanad ke sath usi (Yunus) ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
6008,"ibne-abi Adi ne Shoba se unhon-ne Habib (bin abi Sabit Asadi) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Madina mein they, to mujhey khabar pahunchi ke Kufa mein taaoon phail gaya hai to Ata-bin-Yasar aur doosrey logon ne mujh se kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : jab tum kisi sar zamin mein ho aur wahan taaoon phail jaey to tum us sar zamin se mat niklo aur jab tum ko ye khabar pahunchey ke wo kisi sar zamin mein phail gaya hai to tum usmein mat jao. kaha : maine puchha : (hadis) kis se riwayat ki gaee? un sab ne kaha : Aamir-bin-Sad se wahi ye hadis bayan kartey they. kaha : to main unke yahan pahuncha, unke (ghar ke) logon ne kaha : wo maujood nahi, to main unke bhai Ibrahim bin Sad se mila aur unse malum kya to unhon-ne kaha : main Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas maujood tha jab wo ( mere walid (Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ko hadis bayan kar rahe they. unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : ye bimari saza aur azab hai ya azab ka Baqiya hissa hai jis main tum se pahley ke logon ko mubtala kya gaya tha. to jab ye kisi sar zamin mein phail jaey aur tum wahin ho to wahan se bahar mat niklo aur jab tumhen khabar pahunchey ke ye kisi sar zamin mein hai to usmein mat jao . Habib ne kaha : maine Ibrahim (bin Sad ( se kaha : kya aap ne ( khud ( Usama (Raziallahu anhu) se suna tha wo Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye hadis suna rahe they aur wo iska inkar nahi kar rahe they? unhon-ne kaha : haan."
6009,"ibne-abi Adi ne Shoba se unhon-ne Habib (bin abi Sabit Asadi) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Madina mein they, to mujhey khabar pahunchi ke Kufa mein taaoon phail gaya hai to Ata-bin-Yasar aur doosrey logon ne mujh se kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : jab tum kisi sar zamin mein ho aur wahan taaoon phail jaey to tum us sar zamin se mat niklo aur jab tum ko ye khabar pahunchey ke wo kisi sar zamin mein phail gaya hai to tum usmein mat jao. kaha : maine puchha : (hadis) kis se riwayat ki gaee? un sab ne kaha : Aamir-bin-Sad se wahi ye hadis bayan kartey they. kaha : to main unke yahan pahuncha, unke (ghar ke) logon ne kaha : wo maujood nahi, to main unke bhai Ibrahim bin Sad se mila aur unse malum kya to unhon-ne kaha : main Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas maujood tha jab wo ( mere walid (Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ko hadis bayan kar rahe they. unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : ye bimari saza aur azab hai ya azab ka Baqiya hissa hai jis main tum se pahley ke logon ko mubtala kya gaya tha. to jab ye kisi sar zamin mein phail jaey aur tum wahin ho to wahan se bahar mat niklo aur jab tumhen khabar pahunchey ke ye kisi sar zamin mein hai to usmein mat jao . Habib ne kaha : maine Ibrahim (bin Sad ( se kaha : kya aap ne ( khud ( Usama (Raziallahu anhu) se suna tha wo Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye hadis suna rahe they aur wo iska inkar nahi kar rahe they? unhon-ne kaha : haan."
6010,Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz ke walid ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath ye hadis sunai magar unhon-ne hadis ke shuruat mein Ata-bin-Yasar ka waqia bayan nahi kya.
6011,Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz ke walid ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath ye hadis sunai magar unhon-ne hadis ke shuruat mein Ata-bin-Yasar ka waqia bayan nahi kya.
6012,"Sufiyan ne Habib se, unhon-ne Ibrahim bin Sad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Sad bin Malik , Hazrat Khuzaima bin Sabit aur Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aagey Shoba ki hadis ke ham mana hai."
6013,"Sufiyan ne Habib se, unhon-ne Ibrahim bin Sad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Sad bin Malik , Hazrat Khuzaima bin Sabit aur Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aagey Shoba ki hadis ke ham mana hai."
6014,"Aamash ne Habib se, unhon-ne Ibrahim bin Sad-bin-abi-Waqas se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) baithey huey hadisein bayan kar rahe they. to un donon ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jis tarah un sab ki hadis hai."
6015,"Aamash ne Habib se, unhon-ne Ibrahim bin Sad-bin-abi-Waqas se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) baithey huey hadisein bayan kar rahe they. to un donon ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jis tarah un sab ki hadis hai."
6016,"Shebani ne Habib bin abi Sabit se, unhon-ne Ibrahim bin Sad bin Malik se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se un sabki bayan ki hui hadis ke mutabiq riwayat ki."
6017,"Shebani ne Habib bin abi Sabit se, unhon-ne Ibrahim bin Sad bin Malik se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se un sabki bayan ki hui hadis ke mutabiq riwayat ki."
6018,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne abdul-Hameed bin Abdur-Rehman bin Zaid bin-Khattab se, unhon-ne Abdullah bin-Abdullah-bin Haris bin Nofal se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke saiyedna umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Sham (Syria) ki taraf nikley. jab (Tabook ke maqam ( Sargh par pahunchey to lashkar gaahon ke ameeron mein saiyedna abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke ashaab ne aap se mulaqat ki. aur ye bataya ke Sham (Syria) mein wabaa phail gaee hai. saiyedna Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mere samney muhajireen awwaleen ko bulao. (muhajireen awwaleen wo log hain jinhoney donon qible ki taraf Namaz padhi ho) maine unko bulaya. saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse mashwara liya aur unse bayan kya ke Sham (Syria) ke mulk mein wabaa phaili hui hai. unhon-ne ikhtilaf kya. kuchh ne kaha ke aap aik aham kaam ke liye nikley huey hain isliye ham aap ka lautna munasib nahi samajhtey. kuchh ne kaha ke tumharey sath wo log hain jo aglon mein baqi reh gaey hain aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab hain aur ham unko wabaai mulk mein ley jana munasib nahi samajhtey. saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ab tum log jao. phir kaha ke Ansar ke logon ko bulao. maine unko bulaya to unhon-ne unse mashwara liya. Ansar bhi muhajireen ki chaal chaley aur unhi ki tarah ikhtilaf kya. saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tum log jao. phir kaha ke ab Quraish ke budhon ko bulao jo fateh Makka se pahley ya (fatah ke sath hi) musalman huey hain. maine unko bulaya aur unmein se 2 ne bhi ikhtilaf nahi kya, sab ne yahi kaha ke ham munasib samajhtey hain ke aap logon ko lekar lot jaaiye aur unko wabaa ke samney na kijiye . aakhir saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon mein manaadi kara di ke main subah ko oont par Sawar hunga (aur Madina lautunga) tum bhi Sawar ho jao. saiyedna abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke kya taqdeer se bhaagtey ho? saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke kash! ye baat koi aur kehta (ya agar aur koi kehta to main usko saza deta) {aur saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) bura jantey they unka khilaf karne ko} haan ham Allah ki taqdeer se Allah ki taqdeer ki taraf bhaagtey hain. kya agar tumharey paas oont hon aur tum aik wadi mein jao jiske 2 kinarey hon aik kinara sar-sabz aur shaadab ho aur doosra khushk aur kharaab ho aur tum apne oonton ko sar-sabz aur shaadab kinarey mein charaao to Allah ki taqdeer se charaaya aur jo khushk aur kharaab mein charaao tab bhi Allah ki taqdeer se churaaya (saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka matlab ye hai ke jaisey us charwaahey par koi ilzam nahi hai balke uska amal qaabile-tareef hai ke janwaron ko aaraam diya, aisa hi main bhi apni raiyat ka charaney wala hun to jo mulk achchha malum hota hai udhar le jata hun aur ye kaam taqdeer ke khilaf nahi hai balke theek taqdeere-ilahi hai)? itney mein saiyedna Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur wo kisi kaam ko gaey huey they, unhon-ne kaha ke mere paas to us masle ki daleel maujood hai, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke jab tum suno ke kisi mulk mein waba phaili hai to wahan mat jao aur agar tumharey mulk mein wabaa phailey to bhaago bhi nahi. kaha : is par saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah ka shukr ada kya. phir (agley din) rawaana ho gaey."
6019,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne abdul-Hameed bin Abdur-Rehman bin Zaid bin-Khattab se, unhon-ne Abdullah bin-Abdullah-bin Haris bin Nofal se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke saiyedna umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Sham (Syria) ki taraf nikley. jab (Tabook ke maqam ( Sargh par pahunchey to lashkar gaahon ke ameeron mein saiyedna abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke ashaab ne aap se mulaqat ki. aur ye bataya ke Sham (Syria) mein wabaa phail gaee hai. saiyedna Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mere samney muhajireen awwaleen ko bulao. (muhajireen awwaleen wo log hain jinhoney donon qible ki taraf Namaz padhi ho) maine unko bulaya. saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse mashwara liya aur unse bayan kya ke Sham (Syria) ke mulk mein wabaa phaili hui hai. unhon-ne ikhtilaf kya. kuchh ne kaha ke aap aik aham kaam ke liye nikley huey hain isliye ham aap ka lautna munasib nahi samajhtey. kuchh ne kaha ke tumharey sath wo log hain jo aglon mein baqi reh gaey hain aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab hain aur ham unko wabaai mulk mein ley jana munasib nahi samajhtey. saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ab tum log jao. phir kaha ke Ansar ke logon ko bulao. maine unko bulaya to unhon-ne unse mashwara liya. Ansar bhi muhajireen ki chaal chaley aur unhi ki tarah ikhtilaf kya. saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tum log jao. phir kaha ke ab Quraish ke budhon ko bulao jo fateh Makka se pahley ya (fatah ke sath hi) musalman huey hain. maine unko bulaya aur unmein se 2 ne bhi ikhtilaf nahi kya, sab ne yahi kaha ke ham munasib samajhtey hain ke aap logon ko lekar lot jaaiye aur unko wabaa ke samney na kijiye . aakhir saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon mein manaadi kara di ke main subah ko oont par Sawar hunga (aur Madina lautunga) tum bhi Sawar ho jao. saiyedna abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke kya taqdeer se bhaagtey ho? saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke kash! ye baat koi aur kehta (ya agar aur koi kehta to main usko saza deta) {aur saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) bura jantey they unka khilaf karne ko} haan ham Allah ki taqdeer se Allah ki taqdeer ki taraf bhaagtey hain. kya agar tumharey paas oont hon aur tum aik wadi mein jao jiske 2 kinarey hon aik kinara sar-sabz aur shaadab ho aur doosra khushk aur kharaab ho aur tum apne oonton ko sar-sabz aur shaadab kinarey mein charaao to Allah ki taqdeer se charaaya aur jo khushk aur kharaab mein charaao tab bhi Allah ki taqdeer se churaaya (saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka matlab ye hai ke jaisey us charwaahey par koi ilzam nahi hai balke uska amal qaabile-tareef hai ke janwaron ko aaraam diya, aisa hi main bhi apni raiyat ka charaney wala hun to jo mulk achchha malum hota hai udhar le jata hun aur ye kaam taqdeer ke khilaf nahi hai balke theek taqdeere-ilahi hai)? itney mein saiyedna Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur wo kisi kaam ko gaey huey they, unhon-ne kaha ke mere paas to us masle ki daleel maujood hai, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke jab tum suno ke kisi mulk mein waba phaili hai to wahan mat jao aur agar tumharey mulk mein wabaa phailey to bhaago bhi nahi. kaha : is par saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah ka shukr ada kya. phir (agley din) rawaana ho gaey."
6020,"Mamar ne hamein isi sanad ke sath Malik ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur Mamar ki hadis mein ye alfaz zayed bayan kiye, kaha : aur unhon (hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne un (abu Ubeda (Raziallahu anhu)) se ye bhi kaha : aap ka kya haal hai ke agar wo ( oont ( banjar kinarey par charey aur sar-sabz kinarey ko chhod de to kya aap usey uske ajz aur ghalati par mahmool karengey ? unhon-ne kaha : haan , Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to phir chalein . (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : wo chal kar Madina aaey aur kaha : insha-Allah ! yahi ( kajaawey ( kholney ki, ya kaha : yahi utarney ki jagah hai."
6021,"Mamar ne hamein isi sanad ke sath Malik ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur Mamar ki hadis mein ye alfaz zayed bayan kiye, kaha : aur unhon (hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne un (abu Ubeda (Raziallahu anhu)) se ye bhi kaha : aap ka kya haal hai ke agar wo ( oont ( banjar kinarey par charey aur sar-sabz kinarey ko chhod de to kya aap usey uske ajz aur ghalati par mahmool karengey ? unhon-ne kaha : haan , Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to phir chalein . (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : wo chal kar Madina aaey aur kaha : insha-Allah ! yahi ( kajaawey ( kholney ki, ya kaha : yahi utarney ki jagah hai."
6022,"Yunus ne isi sanad ke sath ibne-Shahab se khabar di, magar unhon-ne kaha : bila shubah Abdullah-bin-Haaris ne unhein hadis sunai aur Abdullah bin-Abdullah nahi kaha."
6023,"Yunus ne isi sanad ke sath ibne-Shahab se khabar di, magar unhon-ne kaha : bila shubah Abdullah-bin-Haaris ne unhein hadis sunai aur Abdullah bin-Abdullah nahi kaha."
6024,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Aamir-bin-Rabeea se, riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Sham (Syria) ki taraf rawana huey, jab Sargh pahunchey to unko ye itlaa mili ke Sham (Syria) mein waba namudaar ho gaee hai. to Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : jab tum kisi ilaaqey mein us (waba) ki khabar suno to wahan na jao aur jab tum kisi ilaaqey mein ho aur wahan waba namudar ho jaey to us waba se bhagney ke liye wahan se na niklo. is par Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Sargh se lot aaey aur ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Salim bin-Abdullah se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis ki wjah se logon ko lekar lot aaey."
6025,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Aamir-bin-Rabeea se, riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Sham (Syria) ki taraf rawana huey, jab Sargh pahunchey to unko ye itlaa mili ke Sham (Syria) mein waba namudaar ho gaee hai. to Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : jab tum kisi ilaaqey mein us (waba) ki khabar suno to wahan na jao aur jab tum kisi ilaaqey mein ho aur wahan waba namudar ho jaey to us waba se bhagney ke liye wahan se na niklo. is par Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Sargh se lot aaey aur ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Salim bin-Abdullah se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis ki wjah se logon ko lekar lot aaey."
6026,"Yunus ne kaha : ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : marz ka kisi doosrey ko chimatna, maah safar ki nahoosat aur maqtool ki khopdi se ullu ka nikalna sab be asl hain to aik erabi (baddu) ne kaha : to phir oonton ka ye haal kyon hota hai ke wo sehra mein aisey phir rahe hotey hain jaisey hiran (sihatmand chaaq chauband), phir aik khaarish zada oont aata hai, unmein shamil hota hai, aur un sab ko khaarish laga deta hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya : pehley oont ko kis ne bimari lagai thi?"
6027,"Yunus ne kaha : ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : marz ka kisi doosrey ko chimatna, maah safar ki nahoosat aur maqtool ki khopdi se ullu ka nikalna sab be asl hain to aik erabi (baddu) ne kaha : to phir oonton ka ye haal kyon hota hai ke wo sehra mein aisey phir rahe hotey hain jaisey hiran (sihatmand chaaq chauband), phir aik khaarish zada oont aata hai, unmein shamil hota hai, aur un sab ko khaarish laga deta hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya : pehley oont ko kis ne bimari lagai thi?"
6028,"Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman wghaira ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi se koi marz khud b-khud nahi chimatta, na bad faali ki koi haqiqat hai na safar ki nahoosat ki aur na khopdi se ullu nikalney ki. to aik dehati kehney laga : ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( aagey ( Yunus ki hadis ki manind (tarah) ( hai.)"
6029,"Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman wghaira ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi se koi marz khud b-khud nahi chimatta, na bad faali ki koi haqiqat hai na safar ki nahoosat ki aur na khopdi se ullu nikalney ki. to aik dehati kehney laga : ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( aagey ( Yunus ki hadis ki manind (tarah) ( hai.)"
6030,"Shuaib ne Zohri se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Sanan bin abi Sanan dauli ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi marz kisi doosrey ko khud b-khud nahi chimatta. to aik dehati khada ho gaya, phir Yunus aur Saleh ki hadis ki manind (tarah) bayan kya aur Shuaib se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Zohri se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Saaib bin Yazeed bin ukhte-Namir ne hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : na kisi se khud-b-khud marz chimatta hai na safar ki nahoosat koi cheez hai aur na khopdi se ullu nikalna."
6031,"Shuaib ne Zohri se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Sanan bin abi Sanan dauli ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi marz kisi doosrey ko khud b-khud nahi chimatta. to aik dehati khada ho gaya, phir Yunus aur Saleh ki hadis ki manind (tarah) bayan kya aur Shuaib se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Zohri se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Saaib bin Yazeed bin ukhte-Namir ne hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : na kisi se khud-b-khud marz chimatta hai na safar ki nahoosat koi cheez hai aur na khopdi se ullu nikalna."
6032,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, ke abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ne unhein hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi se koi marz khud b-khud nahi chimatta aur wo hadis bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bimar oonton wala sihat mand oonton waley ( charwaahey (ke paas oont na ley jaey. abu-Salma ne kaha ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) donon hadisein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kya kartey they, phir Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) (la-adwi) wali hadis bayan karne se ruk gaey aur bimar oonton wala sihat mand oonton waley ke paas ( oont ( na laey. wali hadis par qaaim rahe. to Haris bin abi zubab ne. wo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke chacha ke betey they. kaha : Abu-Hurera ! main tum se suna karta tha, tum iske sath aik aur hadis bayan kartey they jisey bayan karne se ab tum khamosh ho gaey ho. tum kaha kartey they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi se marz khud b-khud nahi chimat-ta to Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne us hadis ko pahchaanney se inkar kar diya aur ye hadis bayan ki. bimar oonton wala sihatmand oonton waley ke paas (oont) na laey. is par Haris ne us mamley mein unke sath takraar ki yahan tak ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ghussey mein aagey aur habshi zaban mein unko na samajh mein aaney wali koi baat kahi, phir Haris se kaha : tumhen pata chala hai ke maine tum se kya kaha hai? unhon-ne kaha : nahi. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tha : main (is se) inkar karta hun. abu-Salma ne kaha : mujhey apni zindagi ki qism ! Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) hamein ye hadis sunaya kartey they. ( لاعدوي ( ) kisi se khud b-khud koi bimari nahi lagti ( mujhey malum nahi ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bhool gaey hain ya aik baat ne dusri ko mansukh kar diya hai."
