6076,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Auf se, unhon-ne Hazrat Muawiya bin-Hakam Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! kuchh kaam aisey they jo ham zamana jahiliyat mein kya kartey they. ham kaahinon ke paas jatey they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum kaahinon ke paas na jaya karo. maine kaha : ham bad shagooni letey they, aap ne farmaya : ye ( badshigooni) mahz aik khayal hai jo koi insan apne dil mein mehsus karta hai, ye tumhen (kisi kaam se) na rokey ."
6077,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Auf se, unhon-ne Hazrat Muawiya bin-Hakam Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! kuchh kaam aisey they jo ham zamana jahiliyat mein kya kartey they. ham kaahinon ke paas jatey they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum kaahinon ke paas na jaya karo. maine kaha : ham bad shagooni letey they, aap ne farmaya : ye ( badshigooni) mahz aik khayal hai jo koi insan apne dil mein mehsus karta hai, ye tumhen (kisi kaam se) na rokey ."
