6080,"Hajjaj sawaaf aur Auzai , donon ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se, unhon-ne Hilal bin abi Memuna se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yasar se, unhon-ne Muawiya bin-Hakam Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Zohri ki abu-Salma se aur unki Muawiya se riwayat ki hui hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, aur Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ki hadis mein ye alfaz zayed bayan kiye, kaha : maine kaha : ham mein aisey log hain jo ( mustaqbil ka haal batane ke liye) lakeerein kheenchtey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : anbiya (Alaihissalam) mein se aik Nabi they jo lakeerein kheenchtey they, jo unki lakeeron se muwafiqat kar gaya to wo theek hai."
