6088,"Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se, riwayat ki : kaha mujhey Ali-bin Husain ( Zainul-Aabedeen ( ne hadis sunai ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon mein se aik Ansari ne mujhey bataya ke aik baar wo log raat ke waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baithey huey they. ke aik sitaarey se kisi cheez ko nishana banaya gaya aur wo roshan ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : jab jahiliyat mein is tarah sitaarey se nishana lagaya jata tha. to tum log kya kaha kartey they? logon ne kaha : Allah aur uska rasool zyada jaanney waley hain ham yahi kaha : kartey they. ke aaj raat kisi azeem insan ki wilaadat hui hai aur koi azeem insan faut hua hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey kisi ki zindagi ya maut ki bina par nishaaney ki taraf nahi chhoda jata, balke hamara rab, uska naam barkat wala aur uncha hai, jab kisi kaam ka faisla farmata hai to arsh waaley ( zor se) tasbeeh kartey hain, phir unse nichey waley aasman ke Farishtey tasbeeh ka wird kartey hain. yahan tak ke tasbeeh ka wird (duniya ke) us aasman tak pahunch jata hai, phir arsh walon ke qareeb ke Farishtey arsh walon se poochhtey hain tumharey parwardigar ne kya farmaaya? wo unhein batatey hain ke usne kya farmaya. phir ( mukhtalif ( aasmanon waley aik doosrey se poochhtey hain, yahan tak ke wo khabar duniya ke us aasman tak pahunch jati hai to jin bhi jaldi se uski kuchh sun-gun uchaktey hain aur apne doston ( kaahinon ( tak de phainktey hain (is khabar ko pahuncha detey hain) jo khabar wo sahi taur par latey hain wo sach to hoti hai lekin wo usmein jhoot milatey aur izafa kar detey hain."
