6090,"Auzai , Yunus aur Maaqil bin Ubaidullah sab ne Zohri se, isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, magar Yunus ne kaha : Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai : mujhey Ansar mein se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne khabar di aur Auzai ki hadis mein hai. lekin wo usmein jhoot milatey hain aur badhatey hain. aur Yunus ki hadis mein hai : lekin wo uncha ley jatey hain (mubaalgha kartey hain) aur badhaatey hain. Yunus ki hadis mein mazeed ye hai : Allah Taala ne farmaya : yahan tak ke jab unke dilon se haibat aur dar ko hata liya jata hai to wo kehtey hain. tumharey rab ne kya kaha ? wo kehtey hain. haq kaha, aur Maaqil ki hadis mein usi ki tarah hai jis tarah Auzai ne kaha : lekin wo usmein jhoot milatey hain aur izafa kartey hain."
