6092,"(hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki ahliya) Safiya ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik ahliya se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke aap ne farmaya : jo shakhs kisi ghaib ki khabrein sunaney waley ke paas aaey aur us se kisi cheez ke barey mein poochhey to chalis (40) raaton tak us shakhs ki Namaz qabool nahi hoti ."
