6097,"Abda bin Sulaiman aur ibne-Numair ne Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne peeth par 2 safaid lakeeron waley sanp ko qatl karne ka hukm diya, kyonke wo basaarat chheen leta hai. aur hamal ko nuqsan pahunchata hai."
