6100,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Salim se, unhon-ne apne walid (hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki : saanpon ko qatl kar do aur) khususan ( 2 safaid lakeeron waley aur dam kate ko, kyonke ye hamal gira detey hain aur basaarat khatm kar detey hain. ( Salim ne) kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko jo bhi sanp milta wo usey mar daltey , aik baar Abu-Lubaaba bin abdul-munzir ya Zaid bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko dekha ke wo aik sanp ka peechha kar rahe they, to unhon-ne kaha : lambi muddat se gharon mein rehney waley saanpon ko (fauri taur par) mar deney se mana kya gaya hai."
6101,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Salim se, unhon-ne apne walid (hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki : saanpon ko qatl kar do aur) khususan ( 2 safaid lakeeron waley aur dam kate ko, kyonke ye hamal gira detey hain aur basaarat khatm kar detey hain. ( Salim ne) kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko jo bhi sanp milta wo usey mar daltey , aik baar Abu-Lubaaba bin abdul-munzir ya Zaid bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko dekha ke wo aik sanp ka peechha kar rahe they, to unhon-ne kaha : lambi muddat se gharon mein rehney waley saanpon ko (fauri taur par) mar deney se mana kya gaya hai."
6102,"Zubaidi ne Zohri se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Salim bin-Abdullah ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap (aawaara kutton ko maar dene ka hukm detey they, aap ne farmatey they : saanpon aur kutton ko maar 2 aur safaid dhaariyon waley aur dam katey sanp ko) zaroor ( maaro , wo donon basaarat zaayel kar detey hain aur haamla aurton ka hamal gira detey hain. Zohri ne kaha : hamara khayal hai ye un donon ke zahar ki bina par hota hai) sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bataaney se aur unse taabeen aur muhaddeseen ne yahi mafhoom liya kya. yahi haqiqat hai, baqi Allah zyada janta hai. Salim ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main aik arsa tak kisi bhi sanp ko dekhta to na chhorta. usey mar deta. aik roz mein muddat se ghar mein rehney waley aik sanp ka peechha kar raha tha ke Zaid bin-Khattab ya abu Lubaba (Raziallahu anhu) mere paas se guzrey to kehney lagey : Abdullah! ruk jao . maine kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein mar deney ka hukm diya hai, unhon-ne kaha : beshak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne muddat se gharon mein rehney waley saanpon (ke qatl ( se roka hai."
6103,"Zubaidi ne Zohri se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Salim bin-Abdullah ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap (aawaara kutton ko maar dene ka hukm detey they, aap ne farmatey they : saanpon aur kutton ko maar 2 aur safaid dhaariyon waley aur dam katey sanp ko) zaroor ( maaro , wo donon basaarat zaayel kar detey hain aur haamla aurton ka hamal gira detey hain. Zohri ne kaha : hamara khayal hai ye un donon ke zahar ki bina par hota hai) sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bataaney se aur unse taabeen aur muhaddeseen ne yahi mafhoom liya kya. yahi haqiqat hai, baqi Allah zyada janta hai. Salim ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main aik arsa tak kisi bhi sanp ko dekhta to na chhorta. usey mar deta. aik roz mein muddat se ghar mein rehney waley aik sanp ka peechha kar raha tha ke Zaid bin-Khattab ya abu Lubaba (Raziallahu anhu) mere paas se guzrey to kehney lagey : Abdullah! ruk jao . maine kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein mar deney ka hukm diya hai, unhon-ne kaha : beshak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne muddat se gharon mein rehney waley saanpon (ke qatl ( se roka hai."
