6116,"Umar-bin Naafe ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : aik din Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) apne ghar ke girey huey hissey ke qareeb maujood they ke unhon-ne achcha sanp ki aik keinchuli dekhi, Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya is sanp ko talash karke qatl kar do. Hazrat abu Lubaba Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne un saanpon ko, jo gharon mein rehtey hain qatl karne se mana farmaya, siwaey dam katey aur 2 safaid dhaariyon waley saanpon ke kyonke yahi 2 sanp hain jo nazar ko khatm kar detey hain aur aurton ke hamal ko nuqsan pahunchaatey hain."
