6124,"abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein Hafs ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Ibrahim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aswad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Mina mein ehram waley aik shakhs ko sanp maarney ka hukm diya."
6125,"abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein Hafs ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Ibrahim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aswad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Mina mein ehram waley aik shakhs ko sanp maarney ka hukm diya."
6126,"Umar-bin Hafs bin Ghiyas ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aamash ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Ibrahim ne Aswad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik ghaar mein they jis tarah Jarir aur abu-Muawiya ki hadis hai."
6127,"Umar-bin Hafs bin Ghiyas ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aamash ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Ibrahim ne Aswad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik ghaar mein they jis tarah Jarir aur abu-Muawiya ki hadis hai."
6128,"imam Malik-bin-Anas ne, ibne- Aflah ke aazad karda ghulam saifii se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Hishaam-bin-Zohra ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Saaib ne bataya ke wo saiyedna Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas unke ghar gaey. abu-Saaib ne kaha ke maine unko Namaz mein paya to baith gaya. mein Namaz padh chukney ka muntazir tha ke itney mein un lakdiyon mein kuchh harkat ki awaz aai jo ghar ke koney mein rakhi thin. maine idhar dekha to aik sanp tha. main uske maarney ko douda to saiyedna abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne ishara kya ke baith jaa. main baith gaya jab Namaz se farigh huey to mujhey aik kothri dikhaatey huey puchha ke ye kothhri dekhtey ho? maine kaha ke haan, unhon-ne kaha ke usmein ham logon mein se aik jawan rehta tha, jiski nai-nai shadi hui thi. ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khandaq ki taraf nikley. wo jawan do-pahar ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat lekar ghar aaya karta tha. aik din Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat mangi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hathiyar lekar ja kyonke mujhey bani Qureza ka dar hai (jinhon ne daghabazi ki thi aur mauqa dekh kar mushrikon ki taraf ho gaey they). us shakhs ne apne hathiyar le liye. jab apne ghar par pahuncha to usne apni biwi ko dekha ke darwazey ke donon patton ke darmyan khadi hai. us ne ghairat se apna neza usey maarney ko uthaya to aurat ne kaha ke apna neza sanbhaal aur andar ja kar dekh to malum hoga ke main kyon nikli hun. wo jawan andar gaya to dekha ke aik bada sanp kundli maarey huey bichhoney par betha hai. jawan ne is par neza uthaya aur usey neze main piro liya, phir nikla aur neza ghar mein gaad diya. wo sanp is par lota iske baad ham nahi jantey ke sanp pahley mara ya jawan pahley Shahid hua. ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Sara qissa bayan kya aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! Allah se dua kijiye ke Allah Taala us jawan ko phir jalaa de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne sathi ke liye bakhshish ki dua karo. phir farmaya ke Madina mein jin rahtey hain jo musalman ho gaey hain, phir agar tum saanpon ko dekho to teen din tak unko khabardar karo, agar teen din ke baad bhi na niklein to unko mar dalo ke wo shaitan hain (yani kaafir jin hain ya shareer sanp hain) ."
6129,"imam Malik-bin-Anas ne, ibne- Aflah ke aazad karda ghulam saifii se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Hishaam-bin-Zohra ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Saaib ne bataya ke wo saiyedna Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas unke ghar gaey. abu-Saaib ne kaha ke maine unko Namaz mein paya to baith gaya. mein Namaz padh chukney ka muntazir tha ke itney mein un lakdiyon mein kuchh harkat ki awaz aai jo ghar ke koney mein rakhi thin. maine idhar dekha to aik sanp tha. main uske maarney ko douda to saiyedna abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne ishara kya ke baith jaa. main baith gaya jab Namaz se farigh huey to mujhey aik kothri dikhaatey huey puchha ke ye kothhri dekhtey ho? maine kaha ke haan, unhon-ne kaha ke usmein ham logon mein se aik jawan rehta tha, jiski nai-nai shadi hui thi. ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khandaq ki taraf nikley. wo jawan do-pahar ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat lekar ghar aaya karta tha. aik din Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat mangi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hathiyar lekar ja kyonke mujhey bani Qureza ka dar hai (jinhon ne daghabazi ki thi aur mauqa dekh kar mushrikon ki taraf ho gaey they). us shakhs ne apne hathiyar le liye. jab apne ghar par pahuncha to usne apni biwi ko dekha ke darwazey ke donon patton ke darmyan khadi hai. us ne ghairat se apna neza usey maarney ko uthaya to aurat ne kaha ke apna neza sanbhaal aur andar ja kar dekh to malum hoga ke main kyon nikli hun. wo jawan andar gaya to dekha ke aik bada sanp kundli maarey huey bichhoney par betha hai. jawan ne is par neza uthaya aur usey neze main piro liya, phir nikla aur neza ghar mein gaad diya. wo sanp is par lota iske baad ham nahi jantey ke sanp pahley mara ya jawan pahley Shahid hua. ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Sara qissa bayan kya aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! Allah se dua kijiye ke Allah Taala us jawan ko phir jalaa de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne sathi ke liye bakhshish ki dua karo. phir farmaya ke Madina mein jin rahtey hain jo musalman ho gaey hain, phir agar tum saanpon ko dekho to teen din tak unko khabardar karo, agar teen din ke baad bhi na niklein to unko mar dalo ke wo shaitan hain (yani kaafir jin hain ya shareer sanp hain) ."
6130,"Jareer-bin-Haazim ne kaha : maine Asma bin Ubaid ko aik aadmi se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, jisey Saaib kaha jata tha. wo hamarey nazdeek abu-Saaib hain. unhon-ne kaha : ham Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas hazir huey, ham baithey huey they jab ham ne unki charpaai ke nichey (kisi cheez ki) harkat ki awaz suni. ham ne dekha to wo aik sanp tha, phir unhon-ne poorey waqiey samet saifii se Imam Malik ki riwayat ki hui hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, aur is mein kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : un gharon mein kuchh makhlooq abad hai. jab tum unmein se koi cheez dekho to teen din tak un par tangi karo (taake wo khud wahan se kahin aur chaley jayen) agar wo pahley jayen (to theek) warna unko mar 2 kyonke phir wo (na janey wala) kaafir hai. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : jao aur apne sathi ko dafn kar do."
6131,"Jareer-bin-Haazim ne kaha : maine Asma bin Ubaid ko aik aadmi se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, jisey Saaib kaha jata tha. wo hamarey nazdeek abu-Saaib hain. unhon-ne kaha : ham Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas hazir huey, ham baithey huey they jab ham ne unki charpaai ke nichey (kisi cheez ki) harkat ki awaz suni. ham ne dekha to wo aik sanp tha, phir unhon-ne poorey waqiey samet saifii se Imam Malik ki riwayat ki hui hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, aur is mein kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : un gharon mein kuchh makhlooq abad hai. jab tum unmein se koi cheez dekho to teen din tak un par tangi karo (taake wo khud wahan se kahin aur chaley jayen) agar wo pahley jayen (to theek) warna unko mar 2 kyonke phir wo (na janey wala) kaafir hai. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : jao aur apne sathi ko dafn kar do."
6132,"ibne- Ajlan ne kaha : mujhey Saifii ne abu-Saaib se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine un (hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu)) ko ye kehtey huey suna, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Madina mein jinon ki kuchh nafri rehti hai jo musalman ho gaey hain jo shakhs un (puraaney) rihaaishon mein se kisi ko dekhey to teen din tak usey ( janey ko) kehta rahe. iske baad agar wo uske samney namudaar ho to usey qatl kar de, kyonke wo shaitan (eman na laney wala jin ( hai."
6133,"ibne- Ajlan ne kaha : mujhey Saifii ne abu-Saaib se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine un (hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu)) ko ye kehtey huey suna, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Madina mein jinon ki kuchh nafri rehti hai jo musalman ho gaey hain jo shakhs un (puraaney) rihaaishon mein se kisi ko dekhey to teen din tak usey ( janey ko) kehta rahe. iske baad agar wo uske samney namudaar ho to usey qatl kar de, kyonke wo shaitan (eman na laney wala jin ( hai."
6134,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba Amr-Naqid Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur ibne-abi-Umar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, Ishaq ne kaha : hamein khabar di jabke doosrey ne kaha : hamein hadis bayan ki, Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne abdul-Hameed bin Juber bin Sheba se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Umme- Sharik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein chhipkaliyon ko mar dalney ka hukm diya. ibne- Shoba ki riwayat main ( unko hukm diya ke bajaey sirf ( hukm diya hai."
6135,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba Amr-Naqid Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur ibne-abi-Umar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, Ishaq ne kaha : hamein khabar di jabke doosrey ne kaha : hamein hadis bayan ki, Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne abdul-Hameed bin Juber bin Sheba se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Umme- Sharik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein chhipkaliyon ko mar dalney ka hukm diya. ibne- Shoba ki riwayat main ( unko hukm diya ke bajaey sirf ( hukm diya hai."
6136,"abu-Taahir ne kaha : hamein ibne- Wahab ne bataya kaha, mujhey ibne-Juraij ne khabar di aur Muhammad-bin Ahmed bin abi Khalaf ne kaha : hamein Rooh ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis sunai aur abd bin Humaid ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Bakr ne bataya, kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey abdul-Hameed bin Juber bin Sheba ne bataya , unhein Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne bataya, unhein Umme- Sharik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se chhipkali ko maarney ke mutaalliq aap ka hukm puchha to aap ne usey mar deney ka hukm diya. Umme- Sharik (Raziallahu anhu) banu-Aamir bin Lui ki aik khatun thin (Muhammad-bin Ahmed) bin abi Khalaf aur abd bin Humaid ki hadis ke alfaz aik hain aur ibne- Wahab ki hadis us se qareeb hai."
6137,"abu-Taahir ne kaha : hamein ibne- Wahab ne bataya kaha, mujhey ibne-Juraij ne khabar di aur Muhammad-bin Ahmed bin abi Khalaf ne kaha : hamein Rooh ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis sunai aur abd bin Humaid ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Bakr ne bataya, kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey abdul-Hameed bin Juber bin Sheba ne bataya , unhein Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne bataya, unhein Umme- Sharik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se chhipkali ko maarney ke mutaalliq aap ka hukm puchha to aap ne usey mar deney ka hukm diya. Umme- Sharik (Raziallahu anhu) banu-Aamir bin Lui ki aik khatun thin (Muhammad-bin Ahmed) bin abi Khalaf aur abd bin Humaid ki hadis ke alfaz aik hain aur ibne- Wahab ki hadis us se qareeb hai."
6138,Aamir-bin-Sad ne apne walid (hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chhipkali ko mar dene ka hukm diya aur iska naam chhoti fasiq rakha.
6139,Aamir-bin-Sad ne apne walid (hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chhipkali ko mar dene ka hukm diya aur iska naam chhoti fasiq rakha.
6140,"abu-Taahir aur Hurmala ne kaha : hamein ibne- Wahab ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey Yunus ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chhipkalii ko 'chhoti fasiq' kaha Hurmala ne (apni) riwayat mein ye izafa kya : (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usko qatl karne ka hukm nahi suna."
6141,"abu-Taahir aur Hurmala ne kaha : hamein ibne- Wahab ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey Yunus ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chhipkalii ko 'chhoti fasiq' kaha Hurmala ne (apni) riwayat mein ye izafa kya : (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usko qatl karne ka hukm nahi suna."
6142,"Khalid-bin-Abdullaah ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne pehli chot mein chhipkali ko qatl kar diya uske liye itni itni nekiyan hain aur jisne dusri chot mein mara uske liye itni itni pehli se kam nekiyan hain aur agar teesri zarb se maara to itni itni nekiyan hain dusri se kam ( bataein.)"
6143,"Khalid-bin-Abdullaah ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne pehli chot mein chhipkali ko qatl kar diya uske liye itni itni nekiyan hain aur jisne dusri chot mein mara uske liye itni itni pehli se kam nekiyan hain aur agar teesri zarb se maara to itni itni nekiyan hain dusri se kam ( bataein.)"
6144,"abu-Awana Jareer, Ismail bin Zakariya aur Sufiyan sab ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, jis tarah Suhel se Khalid ki riwayat hai siwaey akeley Jarir ke unhon-ne apni riwayat ki hui hadis mein kaha : jisne chhipkali ko pehli chot mein mar diya uske liye so nekiyan likhi gain. dusri zarb mein us se kam aur teesri zarb mein us se kam."
6145,"abu-Awana Jareer, Ismail bin Zakariya aur Sufiyan sab ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, jis tarah Suhel se Khalid ki riwayat hai siwaey akeley Jarir ke unhon-ne apni riwayat ki hui hadis mein kaha : jisne chhipkali ko pehli chot mein mar diya uske liye so nekiyan likhi gain. dusri zarb mein us se kam aur teesri zarb mein us se kam."
6146,"Muhammad-bin Sabaah ne kaha : hamein Ismail bin Zakariya ne Suhel se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : mujhey meri behan ( Sauda binte- Abu-Saleh (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : pehli zarb mein 70 nekiyan hain."
6147,"Muhammad-bin Sabaah ne kaha : hamein Ismail bin Zakariya ne Suhel se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : mujhey meri behan ( Sauda binte- Abu-Saleh (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : pehli zarb mein 70 nekiyan hain."
6148,"Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (pahley ( anbiya (Alaihissalam) mein se aik Nabi ko kisi chewnti ne kaat liya, unhon-ne chewntiyon ki poori basti ke barey mein hukm diya to wo jalaa di gaee. is par Allah Taala ne unki taraf wahi ki ke aik chewnti ke kaatney ki wjah se aap ne ummaton mein se aik aisi ummat ( badi aabadi ( ko halaak kar diya, jo Allah ki tasbeeh karti thi?"
6149,"Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (pahley ( anbiya (Alaihissalam) mein se aik Nabi ko kisi chewnti ne kaat liya, unhon-ne chewntiyon ki poori basti ke barey mein hukm diya to wo jalaa di gaee. is par Allah Taala ne unki taraf wahi ki ke aik chewnti ke kaatney ki wjah se aap ne ummaton mein se aik aisi ummat ( badi aabadi ( ko halaak kar diya, jo Allah ki tasbeeh karti thi?"
6150,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (pahley ( anbiya (Alaihissalam) mein se aik Nabi aik darakht ke nichey (aaraam karne ke liye sawari se) utrey to aik chewnti ne unko kaat liya. unhon-ne iske poorey bil ke barey mein hukm diya, usey bil se nikal diya gaya phir hukm diya unko jalaa diya gaya. Allah Taala ne unki taraf wahi ki ke aap ne aik hi chewnti ko kyon ( saza ( na (di?)"
6151,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (pahley ( anbiya (Alaihissalam) mein se aik Nabi aik darakht ke nichey (aaraam karne ke liye sawari se) utrey to aik chewnti ne unko kaat liya. unhon-ne iske poorey bil ke barey mein hukm diya, usey bil se nikal diya gaya phir hukm diya unko jalaa diya gaya. Allah Taala ne unki taraf wahi ki ke aap ne aik hi chewnti ko kyon ( saza ( na (di?)"
6152,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, phir unhon-ne kuchh hadisein zikr kin, unmein se aik ye hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (pahley) anbiya (Alaihissalam) mein se aik Nabi aik darakht ke nichey letey they, unhein aik chewnti ne kaat liya, unhon-ne unki poori aabadi ke barey mein hukm diya, usey nichey se (khodkar) nikal liya gaya, phir uske barey mein hukm diya to us (poori aabadi) ko aag se jalaa diya gaya. to Allah Taala ne unki taraf wahi ki, (is aik hi ko kyon ( saza ( na ( di ? ("
6153,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, phir unhon-ne kuchh hadisein zikr kin, unmein se aik ye hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (pahley) anbiya (Alaihissalam) mein se aik Nabi aik darakht ke nichey letey they, unhein aik chewnti ne kaat liya, unhon-ne unki poori aabadi ke barey mein hukm diya, usey nichey se (khodkar) nikal liya gaya, phir uske barey mein hukm diya to us (poori aabadi) ko aag se jalaa diya gaya. to Allah Taala ne unki taraf wahi ki, (is aik hi ko kyon ( saza ( na ( di ? ("
6154,"Juweriya bin Asma ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik aurat ko billi ke sabab se azab diya gaya, us ne billi ko qaid karke rakha yahan tak ke wo mar gaee. wo aurat uski wjah se jahannam mein chali gaee, us aurat ne jab billi ko qaid kya to na usko khilaaya-pilaya aur na usko chhoda hi ke wo zamin ke andar aur uper rehney waley chhotey chhotey janwar kha leti."
6155,"Juweriya bin Asma ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik aurat ko billi ke sabab se azab diya gaya, us ne billi ko qaid karke rakha yahan tak ke wo mar gaee. wo aurat uski wjah se jahannam mein chali gaee, us aurat ne jab billi ko qaid kya to na usko khilaaya-pilaya aur na usko chhoda hi ke wo zamin ke andar aur uper rehney waley chhotey chhotey janwar kha leti."
6156,"Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, isi tarah ( Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne) Saeed Maqbari se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us hadis ke ham mana hadis riwayat ki."
6157,"Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, isi tarah ( Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne) Saeed Maqbari se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us hadis ke ham mana hadis riwayat ki."
6158,"Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi riwayat ki."
6159,"Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi riwayat ki."
6160,"Abda ne Hisham (bin Urwa) se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik aurat ko billi ke mamley mein azab diya gaya. us aurat ne na usey khilaya na pilaya aur na usko chhoda ke wo zamin ke chhotey janwar kha leti ."
6161,"Abda ne Hisham (bin Urwa) se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik aurat ko billi ke mamley mein azab diya gaya. us aurat ne na usey khilaya na pilaya aur na usko chhoda ke wo zamin ke chhotey janwar kha leti ."
6162,"abu-Muawiya aur Khalid-bin Haris ne hamein hadis sunai kaha : hamein Hisham ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, un donon ki hadis mein hai is aurat ne usey baandh diya aur abu-Muawia ki hadis mein hai : hashraatul-arz (kha leti)"
6163,"abu-Muawiya aur Khalid-bin Haris ne hamein hadis sunai kaha : hamein Hisham ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, un donon ki hadis mein hai is aurat ne usey baandh diya aur abu-Muawia ki hadis mein hai : hashraatul-arz (kha leti)"
6164,"Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Hisham ki us hadis ke ham-mana riwayat ki."
6165,"Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Hisham ki us hadis ke ham-mana riwayat ki."
6166,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, unki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
6167,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, unki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
6168,"Abu-Saleh samaan ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik baar aik shakhs rastey mein chala ja raha tha usko shadeed piyaas lagi , usey aik kunwaan mila wo us kuwein mein utra aur pani piya, phir wo kuwein se nikla to uske samney aik kutta zor-zor se haanp raha tha, piyaas ki wjah se keechad chaat raha tha, us shakhs ne (dil mein) kaha : ye kutta bhi piyaas se usi haalat ko pahuncha hai jo meri hui thi. wo kuwein mein utra aur apne mozey ko pani se bharaa phir usko munh se pakda yahan tak ke uper chadh aaya, phir us ne kuttey ko pani pilaya . Allah Taala ne usey us neki ka badla diya usko bakhsh diya. logon ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! hamarey liye un janwaron mein ajr hai? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nami rakhney waley har jigar main ( kisi bhi jaandaar ka ho. ( ajr hai."
